causing trouble for you?

622
00:29:13,540 --> 00:29:14,460
It's been five years.

623
00:29:15,140 --> 00:29:16,140
I've long let it go.

624
00:29:17,620 --> 00:29:18,620
Rest well.

625
00:29:18,860 --> 00:29:19,740
