634
00:29:38,700 --> 00:29:40,300
How can I focus on anything else?

635
00:29:40,730 --> 00:29:41,700
So, what do you want?

636
00:29:42,720 --> 00:29:44,340
If you want me to treat you,

637
00:29:44,780 --> 00:29:46,740
